Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N- 　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.06,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:23.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:29.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:49.22,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:56.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:01.90,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.42,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:11.36,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:15.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:19.25,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.73,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:26.13,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:29.79,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:30.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.61,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:39.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:43.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不见的羽翼引导
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:23.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遥远的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:29.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不见的未来依旧在等待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不愿清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:49.22,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包围 谁也逃不出这个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变幻不定的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:56.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:01.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.42,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:11.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方听闻的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:15.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震动鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:19.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:26.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我渐渐清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:29.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:30.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.61,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里不断变化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:39.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的伤口 是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:43.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因为你和Burst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N- 　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　\N
